{{vgname|捉鬼敢死队|en=Ghostbusters|cn=捉鬼敢死队|tw=魔鬼剋星}}是[[Fireforge|FireForge Games]]开发，动视发行的动作冒险游戏，为2016年[[魔鬼剋星_(2016年電影)|同名电影]]的改编游戏。该游戏有四个玩家合作游戏模式，让玩家控制捉鬼敢死队角色打败作为敌人的鬼。该游戏于2016年7月12日在Microsoft Windows，PlayStation 4和Xbox One平台上发行。<ref>{{cite web|last1=McWhertor|first1=Michael|title=The new Ghostbusters video game won't feature the new cast (or the old one)|url=http://www.polygon.com/2016/4/14/11433572/ghostbusters-2016-video-game|website=Polygon|accessdate=2016-05-22|date=2016-04-14|archive-date=2020-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108093826/http://www.polygon.com/2016/4/14/11433572/ghostbusters-2016-video-game|dead-url=no}}</ref>开发商FireForge在游戏发布后三天因1200万美元债务而申请破产。<ref name="NZGamer">{{Cite web |url=http://nzgamer.com/news/10380/ghostbusters-developer-fireforge-goes-bankrupt.html |title=存档副本 |access-date=2016-08-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160802210028/http://nzgamer.com/news/10380/ghostbusters-developer-fireforge-goes-bankrupt.html |archive-date=2016-08-02 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>

